---
// Problem copy is inline — only used once on the homepage
---

<section class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-24 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <div
      class="reveal inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 text-primary text-lg font-semibold"
    >
      The Problem
    </div>
    <h2
      class="reveal text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-4"
    >
      Your clients are invisible in AI search
    </h2>
    <p class="reveal text-xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Millions of buyers now ask AI instead of Google. If your client's brand
      isn't in the answer, it doesn't exist.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div
      class="reveal bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm text-center"
    >
      <div
        class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-red-500/10"
      >
        <svg
          class="h-6 w-6 text-red-400"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">
        Zero visibility
      </h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        AI engines answer buyer queries without mentioning your client's brand.
        Competitors get the citation instead.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="reveal bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm text-center"
    >
      <div
        class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10"
      >
        <svg
          class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-400"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">
        No way to measure it
      </h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        Google Search Console tracks SERPs. Nothing tracks AI answers. You're
        flying blind on the fastest-growing search channel.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div
      class="reveal bg-card p-8 rounded-2xl border border-border shadow-sm text-center"
    >
      <div
        class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-blue-500/10"
      >
        <svg
          class="h-6 w-6 text-blue-400"
          fill="none"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
        >
          <path
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
            d="M2.25 18L9 11.25l4.306 4.307a11.95 11.95 0 015.814-5.519l2.74-1.22m0 0l-5.94-2.28m5.94 2.28l-2.28 5.941"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">
        Clients are asking questions
      </h3>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground">
        "Are we showing up in ChatGPT?" Your agency needs an answer — and a
        dashboard to prove it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
